Azeri Soldier Kills Seven Others at Army Base, Turan Reports

-- B y   Z u l f u g a r   A g a y e v
-- 
2011-02-21T09:54:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/azeri-soldier-kills-seven-others-at-army-base-turan-reports.html
An Azeri soldier shot at least seven
members of his unit to death with a machine-gun yesterday, Turan
reported, citing unidentified people with knowledge of the
incident.  The shooting occurred at a military base in western  Azerbaijan  on the border with the Armenian-controlled Azeri
region of Kalbajar, the Baku-based news service reported today.  Azerbaijan’s Defense Ministry and Prosecutor General’s
Office confirmed the deaths, without providing further
information.  In a separate incident, an Azeri soldier was killed and
another wounded by Armenian fire, Teymur Abdullayev, a Defense
Ministry spokesman, said by telephone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zulfugar Agayev in Baku via the Moscow news room at  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
